    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n6036" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μέλαθρον</span></b> , <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">μελαθρόφι</span>: <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">beam</span>, crossbeam of
          a house, supporting rafters and roof; these beams passed through the
          wall and projected externally, hence <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἐπὶ
            προὔχοντι μελάθρῳ</span>, <i><span class="en">Od.
            19.544</span></i>; then <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">roof</span> (tectum), and in wider sense
            <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">dwelling, mansion</span>, <i><span class="en">Il.
            9.640</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
